openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: API
  version: v1
paths:

    get:

        '200':
          description: ''

            application/json:
              schema:
                anyOf:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/CarColor'

            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CarColorList'

      properties:
        color:
          type: string
          enum:
            - black
            - white
            - red
            - green
            - blue

      properties:
        color:
          type: string

          enum:
            - black
            - white
            - red
            - green
            - blue
    CarColorList:
      properties:
        color:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            enum:
              - black
              - white
              - red
              - green
              - blue
    CarColorListNullable:
      properties:
        color:
          type: array
          nullable: true
          items:
            type: string
            enum:
              - black
              - white
              - red
              - green
              - blue
    CarColorRequired:
      properties:
        color:
          type: string
          enum:
            - black
            - white
            - red
            - green
            - blue
      required:
        - color
    CarColorNullable:
      properties:
        color:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          enum:
            - black
            - white
            - red
            - green
            - blue
